    • Constructor Detail

      • BankAccountTokenParams

        public BankAccountTokenParams(java.lang.String country,
                              java.lang.String currency,
                              java.lang.String accountNumber,
                              BankAccountTokenParams.Type accountHolderType,
                              java.lang.String accountHolderName,
                              java.lang.String routingNumber)

        Create a bank account token

        Parameters:
        country -

        The country in which the bank account is located.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-country

        currency -

        The currency the bank account is in. This must be a country/currency pairing that Stripe supports.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-currency

        accountNumber -

        The account number for the bank account, in string form. Must be a checking account.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-account_number

        accountHolderType -

        The type of entity that holds the account. This can be either individual or company. This field is required when attaching the bank account to a Customer object.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-account_holder_type

        accountHolderName -

        The name of the person or business that owns the bank account. This field is required when attaching the bank account to a Customer object.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-account_holder_name

        routingNumber -

        The routing number, sort code, or other country-appropriate institution number for the bank account. For US bank accounts, this is required and should be the ACH routing number, not the wire routing number. If you are providing an IBAN for account_number, this field is not required.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_bank_account#create_bank_account_token-bank_account-routing_number

        See Also:
        Create a bank account token
